erial relative to >80% of solar twins (at\n2$\\sigma$ confidence), suggesting a possible signpost for planetary systems\nlike our own.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Feb 2018 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Aug 2018 14:28:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-10"}
