densities and the 21cm signal during\nthe EoR. However, a more detailed interpretation of the bias parameters may\nrequire a description of non-local contributions to the bias model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Feb 2018 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Oct 2018 16:55:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 8 Oct 2018 19:58:06 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 31 May 2019 15:21:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-19"}
